}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== :This product has alternate models of K33118USB and K33118B.
This hub identifies as two 05e3:0608 devices to the host system.
The copyright date on the hub's package is 2008. :This is presumed to be around the correct time frame of release..
The power adapter included with the hub is a '''DVE''' ''DSA-15P-05 US 050125'' :(100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz 0.5A -> 5VDC 2.5A).
